OL,3,CCharity cycle involving wife of Doddie
OL,4,CWeir sets off with #1m already raised
OL,6,FA charity cycling team including the
OL,7,Fwife of late rugby legend and motor
OL,8,Fneurone disease (MND) campaigner
OL,9,FDoddie Weir has raised more than #1
OL,10,Fmillion for the foundation in his name.
OL,12,FThe Doddie's Triple Crown 2026 team
OL,13,Fpassed the milestone on Tuesday ` the
OL,14,Fsame day their 750-mile pedal from
OL,15,FScotland to Dublin officially began.
OL,17,FRugby stars Rob Wainwright, Andy Nicol
OL,18,Fand Gordon D'Arcy are part of the
OL,19,Fgroup of hundreds of cyclists taking
OL,20,Fpart, alongside world record-breaking
OL,21,Fcyclist Mark Beaumont.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
