PN,35702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1773249074
OL,3,CCharity cycle involving wife of Doddie
OL,4,CWeir sets off with #1m already raised
OL,6,FThey were joined by Kathy Weir, 55,
OL,7,Fwho is taking on her first major
OL,8,Ffundraising challenge, as they set off
OL,9,Ffrom Melrose in the Scottish Borders.
OL,11,FThey aim to reach Dublin on Friday,
OL,12,Fahead of the Ireland v Scotland Six
OL,13,FNations tie on Saturday.
OL,15,FScottish Borders star Doddie Weir died
OL,16,Fin November 2022 aged 52 after living
OL,17,Fwith MND for more than six years.
OL,19,FHe founded the My Name'5 Doddie
OL,20,FFoundation in 2017 to fund research
OL,21,Finto MND.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
