SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1773249074
OL,3,CCharity cycle involving wife of Doddie
OL,4,CWeir sets off with #1m already raised
OL,6,FWainwright, a former teammate of
OL,7,FWeir's, said: "It has to be painful.
OL,8,FThree 180 to 200-mile days in a row is
OL,9,Frelentless - the lack of sleep, the
OL,10,Fearly starts, the cumulative fatigue.
OL,11,FIf we get headwinds and rain the whole
OL,12,Fway, it'll be brutal. But there has to
OL,13,Fbe a challenge.
OL,15,F"We've done quite a few of these big
OL,16,Frides now and it's great to see some
OL,17,Ffamiliar faces join us, as well as
OL,18,Fsome new ones too. We are so pleased
OL,19,Fthat Kathy is taking part.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1773249074
OL,3,CCharity cycle involving wife of Doddie
OL,4,CWeir sets off with #1m already raised
OL,6,F"We're all pedalling for Doddie to
OL,7,Ffinish his mission to end MND. All
OL,8,Ffunds raised will help My Name'5
OL,9,FDoddie Foundation do that and we're
OL,10,Fgrateful for every penny."
OL,12,FMother-of-three Mrs Weir said: "Doddie
OL,13,Fwas so good at shouting from the
OL,14,Frooftops and making sure everyone knew
OL,15,Fabout this disease. Rob and so many
OL,16,Fothers have done so much to keep
OL,17,Fmomentum, continue fundraising and
OL,18,Fbring us closer to a cure.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
